import { Box } from "@mui/material";
import MyTypography from "../../../components/MyTypography"
import Navigator from '../../../components/Navigator'

const Header = () =>{
    return(
        <Box sx={{margin: "16px 0px;", display:'flex', justifyContent:'center', alignItems:'center', height:'486px', flexDirection:'column',textAlign:'center' }}>
            {/* <Typography sx={{fontSize:"24px", letterSpacing:'6px', fontFamily:'Raleway', margin:'10px 0', fontWeight:'400',opacity:'0.5'}}>
                PHOTOGRAPHER
            </Typography>
            <Typography sx={{fontSize:"36px", letterSpacing:'6px', fontFamily:'Raleway', margin:'10px 0', fontWeight:'400',opacity:'0.5'}}>
                John Doe
            </Typography> */}
            <MyTypography 
                text="PHOTOGRAPHER" 
                size="24px"
                letterSpacing="6px"
                fontFamily="Raleway"
                margin="10px 0"
                fontWeight=""
            />
            <Navigator/>
        </Box>
    );
}

export default Header
